<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَبَعْدُ فَإِنِّي سَوْفَ أُنْظِمُ جُمْلَةٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مِن الأَدَبِ الْمَأْثُورِ عَنْ خَيْرِ مُرْشِدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مِن السُّنَّةِ الْغَرَّاءِ أَوْ مِنْ كِتَابِ مَنْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>تَقَدَّسَ عَنْ قَوْلِ الْغُواةِ وَجُحَّدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ومِنْ قَوْلِ أَهْلِ الْعِلْمِ مِنْ عُلَمَائِنَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَئِمَّةِ أَهْلِ السِّلْمِ مِنْ كُلِّ أَمْجَدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لَعَلَّ إِلَهَ الْعَرْشِ يَنْفَعُنَا بِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيُنْزِلُنَا فِي الْحَشْرِ فِي خَيْرِ مَقْعَدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الأمن لَهُ فِي الْعِلْمِ وَالدِّينِ رَغْبَةٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لِيُصْغِ بِقَلْبٍ حَاضِرٍ مُتَرَصِّدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيَقْبَلَ نُصْحًا مِنْ شَفِيقٍ عَلَى الْوَرَى<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>حَرِيصٍ عَلَى زَجْرِ الأَنَامِ عَنِ الرَّدِيِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَعِنْدِيَ مِن عِلْمِ الْحَدِيثِ أَمَانَةٌ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>سَأَبْذُلُهَا جُهْدِي فَأَهْدِي وَأَهْتَدِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَلا كُلُّ مَنْ رَامَ السَّلامَةَ فَلْيَصُنْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>جَوَارِحَهُ عَنْ مَا نَهَى اللهُ يَهْتَدِي<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>يَكُبُ الْفَتَى فِي النَّارِ حَصْدُ لِسَانِهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِرْسَالُ طَرْفِ الْمَرْءِ أنْكَى فَقَيِّدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَطَرْفُ الْفَتَى يَا صَاحِ رَائِدُ فَرْجِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَمُتْعِبُهُ فَاغْضُضْهُ ما اسْطَعْتَ تَهْتَدِي<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ بُهْتٌ واغْتِيَابٌ نَمِيْمَةٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>